<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="64" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1437,152,380]" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,314,340]" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[870,955,315,340]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">quadra</emphasis>
(= rectangular), referring to the shape of the distal part of the valva.
</paragraph>
